def if_decimal_is_divisible(binary):
    def fibonacci(n):
        fib = [0, 1]
        for i in range(2, n+1):
            fib.append(fib[i-1] + fib[i-2])
        return fib[n]

    decimal = int(binary, 2)
    fibonacci_7 = fibonacci(7)
    
    return decimal % fibonacci_7 == 0
